OL,7,FHe then drove forward with the police
OL,8,Fcar still attached to the truck for 27
OL,9,Fseconds, before the vehicle became
OL,10,Fdetached and the defendant drove off.
OL,11,FVideo footage was played to the court
OL,12,Fof the collision which showed the
OL,13,Fdefendant reversing into the officer,
OL,14,Fwho suffered injuries including
OL,15,Freddening, bruising, soreness and
OL,16,Ftenderness.
OL,18,FSmith, of Fountain Court, Abertillery,
OL,19,Fwas later arrested and pleaded guilty
OL,20,Fto dangerous driving and theft.
