OL,7,FIn mitigation, Hashim Salmman said his
OL,8,Fclient had previously attempted
OL,9,Fsuicide following the tragic loss of a
OL,10,Fchild.
OL,12,FIn his sentencing remarks, Judge
OL,13,FDaniel Williams told the defendant he
OL,14,Fcaused "personal injury and
OL,15,Fsubstantial damage", and only an
OL,16,Fimmediate custodial sentence was
OL,17,Fappropriate.JSmith was sentenced to 16
OL,18,Fmonths imprisonment. He was also
OL,19,Fdisqualified from driving for a total
OL,20,Fof 20 months.
